# geometry) but are regenerable from Spots.bin + the C
# ``SaveBinDataScanning`` step in test_pf_hedm.py. They're produced
# locally by ``build.py`` and consumed by the P5c parity test, which
# skips with a helpful message when they're absent.
Data.bin
nData.bin
